      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; simulation and experimental inputs confirmed nominally equivalent by inspection.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment not required at MRL 2. Simulation boundary conditions confirmed to match experimental setup by inspection of test protocol and simulation input files."
